stories.title: Sri Lanka win with consummate ease
stories.summary:
TANGIER-With three innings of substance from the first four top order
batsmen, Sri Lanka marched to their third win in four games with
consummate ease, reaching the target with six wickets to spare and eight
of the regulation 50 overs remaining
